premise_source_doc_sentence: FXX is an American digital cable and satellite television channel launched on September 2 , 2013 , owned by 21st Century Fox through FX Networks , LLC .
It is the sister channel of the larger network , FX .
The channel 's programming focuses on original and acquired comedy series , some dramatic programs , acquired children 's series , and feature films .
FXX launched at 7:00 a.m. Eastern/6 :00 a.m. Central on September 2 , 2013 , replacing Fox Soccer .

The channel is best known for setting the record for the longest continuous marathon in the history of television , which featured every single episode of The Simpsons that had already been released at the time , which numbered over 550 .
This record has since been broken .
As of July 2015 , approximately 78,498,000 households in the United States  (  67.4 % of those with television  )  receive FXX .
